{"date":"1980-03-19","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/db/da/22704_QRrQ3.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/db/da/22704_QRrQ3.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/db/da/22704_QRrQ3.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/db/da/22704_QRrQ3.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/db/da/22704_QRrQ3.jpg"},"summary":"本片改编自安徒生童话《牧羊女和扫烟囱的工人》。国王密室的墙壁上画着一位美丽的牧羊姑娘和一个扫烟囱的小伙子。两人坠入爱河，相约从画中出来，并在一只聪明的小鸟的帮助下逃出了王宫。但是国王的画像也活了过来。国王不但掳走了牧羊姑娘，又把扫烟囱的小伙子和小鸟一起打入地牢。最终小鸟和地下的义民一起推翻了残暴的国王，救出了牧羊姑娘。\r\n\r\n本片有两个版本，一个是50年代上映版本，当时由于导演编剧与制作人闹翻，没做完的影片被强行拿去上映，命名为《扫烟囱工人与牧羊女》（日：《斜眼暴君》）。后来导演编剧拿回了影片版权，重制了影片，在80年代重新上映，命名为《国王与小鸟》。","name":"Le Roi et l'oiseau","name_cn":"国王与小鸟","tags":[{"name":"法国","count":39,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980","count":31,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Paul_Grimault","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"爱情","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"自由","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电影","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"经典","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冒险","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"法国动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"非日本","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Raymond_Bussières","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"PaulGrimault","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"アニメ映画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"七分","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"非日本動畫電影","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"长片","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"劇場版1","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"老害最爱","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"AM","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1952","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"JeanMartin","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"LesGémeaux","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Jacques_Prévert","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电视","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"fantasy","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80年代","count":1,"t